<div style="text-align:left; position:relative; left:4px; top:2px; margin:0; font-family:'Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif'" about="#mwt5" typeof="mw:Transclusion" id="mwBw" data-mw="{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Feature Articles All","href":"./Template:Feature_Articles_All"},"params":{},"i":0}}]}">
<p><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" resource="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bluebg_rounded.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/46/Bluebg_rounded.png" decoding="async" data-file-width="350" data-file-height="25" data-file-type="bitmap" height="25" width="350" class="mw-file-element"></span></span></p>
<div style="position:absolute; left:5px; top:-6px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" resource="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:HSutvald2.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/HSutvald2.svg/40px-HSutvald2.svg.png" decoding="async" data-file-width="156" data-file-height="156" data-file-type="drawing" height="38" width="38" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/HSutvald2.svg/60px-HSutvald2.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/HSutvald2.svg/120px-HSutvald2.svg.png 2x" class="mw-file-element"></span></span></div>
<div style="position:absolute; left:40px; top:-5px;"><div style="font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding:.15em .4em;">Nyati siwo woɖe ɖe go</div></div></div><span about="#mwt5">
</span><div style="padding-left:10px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:2px; font-size:100%" about="#mwt5">
<figure class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img resource="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/40/Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg/250px-Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg" decoding="async" data-file-width="1821" data-file-height="1356" data-file-type="bitmap" height="186" width="250" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/40/Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg/500px-Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/40/Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg/500px-Jerry_Rawlings_2.jpg 2x" class="mw-file-element"></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p><b>Jerry John Rawlings</b> si wodzi <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Masa_22?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Masa 22 (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Masa 22"]}}">Masa 22</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/1947?action=edit&redlink=1" title="1947 (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["1947"]}}">1947</a> me, nye <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gana" title="Gana">Ghana</a> asrafomegã, yameʋukula, kple dunyahela si kplɔ dukɔa kpuie le ƒe 1979 me eye emegbe tso ƒe 1981 va se ɖe ƒe 2001 me. Exɔ ŋgɔ na asrafowo ƒe dziɖuɖu vaseɖe ƒe 1993 me eye emegbe wòwɔ dɔ zi eve abe Ghana ƒe dukplɔla si woti le demokrasimɔ nu ene. Eyae nye kplɔla si nɔ anyi ɣeyiɣi didi wu le Ghana ƒe ŋutinya me, eye wòɖu dukɔa dzi ƒe 19 sɔŋ. Etrɔ megbe le Adeɛmekpɔxe 12, 2020 me.</p>
<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerry_Rawlings" title="Jerry Rawlings">Xlẽ yi edzi le afisia...</a><div align="right" style="font-size:95%;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Featured_Articles" title="Wikipedia:Featured Articles">Nyati Siwo Woɖe Ðe Go</a></div></div><span about="#mwt5">
</span><p about="#mwt5"><br style="clear:both;"></p><span about="#mwt5">

</span><div style="text-align:left; position:relative; left:4px; top:2px; margin:0; font-family:'Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif'" about="#mwt5">
<p><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" resource="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bluebg_rounded.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/46/Bluebg_rounded.png" decoding="async" data-file-width="350" data-file-height="25" data-file-type="bitmap" height="25" width="350" class="mw-file-element"></span></span></p>
<div style="position:absolute; left:5px; top:-6px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" resource="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:HSbra2.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/HSbra2.svg/40px-HSbra2.svg.png" decoding="async" data-file-width="156" data-file-height="156" data-file-type="drawing" height="38" width="38" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/HSbra2.svg/60px-HSbra2.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/HSbra2.svg/120px-HSbra2.svg.png 2x" class="mw-file-element"></span></span></div>
<div style="position:absolute; left:40px; top:-5px;"><div style="font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding:.15em .4em;">Nyati nyuiwo</div></div></div><span about="#mwt5">
</span><div style="padding-left:10px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:2px; font-size:100%" about="#mwt5">
<figure class="mw-default-size mw-halign-left" typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Ghana.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img resource="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Ghana.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Flag_of_Ghana.svg/250px-Flag_of_Ghana.svg.png" decoding="async" data-file-width="900" data-file-height="600" data-file-type="drawing" height="167" width="250" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Flag_of_Ghana.svg/500px-Flag_of_Ghana.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Flag_of_Ghana.svg/500px-Flag_of_Ghana.svg.png 2x" class="mw-file-element"></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>

<p><b>Gana</b> nye <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afrika" title="Afrika">Afrika</a> dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afrika_ƒe_ɣetoɖoƒe?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe"]}}">Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe</a> lɔƒo. Gana do liƒo kple <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Togo" title="Togo">Togo</a> kple, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nyiɖu_Ƒuta" title="Nyiɖu Ƒuta">Nyiɖu Ƒuta</a> kpakple <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burkina_Faso" title="Burkina Faso">Burkina Faso</a>. Aƒu si woyɔna be <i><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gulf_of_Guinea?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Gulf of Guinea (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Gulf of Guinea"]}}">Gulf of Guinea</a></i> la le eƒe anyiehe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 32,833,031 lɔƒo (2016).
Woɖo Gana tso <i>Gold Coast</i> kpakple <i>British Togoland</i> si nɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Gana dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le Tedoxe 6 dzi, le ƒe 1957 me. Gana ƒe fiadzue nye <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Accra" title="Accra">Accra</a>.</p>
<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gana" title="Gana">Xlẽ yi edzi le afisia.....</a><div align="right" style="font-size:95%;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Good_Articles?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Wikipedia:Good Articles (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Wikipedia:Good Articles"]}}">Nyati Siwo Woɖe Ðe Go</a></div></div><span about="#mwt5">
</span><p about="#mwt5"><br style="clear:both;"></p><span about="#mwt5">

</span><div style="text-align:left; position:relative; left:4px; top:2px; margin:0; font-family:'Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif'" about="#mwt5">
<p><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" resource="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bluebg_rounded.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/46/Bluebg_rounded.png" decoding="async" data-file-width="350" data-file-height="25" data-file-type="bitmap" height="25" width="350" class="mw-file-element"></span></span></p>

</span><div style="padding-left:10px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:2px; font-size:100%" about="#mwt5">
<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="240" style="margin: 0 0 1em 1em; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;" align="right">

<p><b>Volta Region (Amugã Nutome)</b> si woyɔna tsa be <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Togoland?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Togoland (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Togoland"]}}">Togoland</a> alo <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_Togoland?action=edit&redlink=1" title="British Togoland (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["British Togoland"]}}">British Togoland</a> nye <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghana" title="Ghana" class="mw-redirect">Ghana</a> ƒe nuto wuiade wo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele ɣetoɖoe kpadzi ne <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Togo" title="Togo">Togo</a> eye le ɣedzeƒe kpadzi na Amuga tɔsisi la. Efe toxɔdue nye <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ho,_Ghana?action=edit&redlink=1" title="Ho, Ghana (wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" data-mw-i18n="{"title":{"lang":"x-page","key":"red-link-title","params":["Ho, Ghana"]}}">Ho</a>.</p>

    Tso Wikipedia
    Woezɔ̃ va Eʋe Wikipedia dzi!
    Sidzedze ƒe dɔwɔƒe si woate ŋu azã faa, afisi amesiame ate ŋu atsɔ eƒe sidzedze akpe ɖe eŋu le.

    Nyati siwo woɖe ɖe go

    Jerry John Rawlings si wodzi Masa 22, 1947 me, nye Ghana asrafomegã, yameʋukula, kple dunyahela si kplɔ dukɔa kpuie le ƒe 1979 me eye emegbe tso ƒe 1981 va se ɖe ƒe 2001 me. Exɔ ŋgɔ na asrafowo ƒe dziɖuɖu vaseɖe ƒe 1993 me eye emegbe wòwɔ dɔ zi eve abe Ghana ƒe dukplɔla si woti le demokrasimɔ nu ene. Eyae nye kplɔla si nɔ anyi ɣeyiɣi didi wu le Ghana ƒe ŋutinya me, eye wòɖu dukɔa dzi ƒe 19 sɔŋ. Etrɔ megbe le Adeɛmekpɔxe 12, 2020 me.

    Xlẽ yi edzi le afisia...
    Nyati Siwo Woɖe Ðe Go


    Nyati nyuiwo

    Gana nye Afrika dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo. Gana do liƒo kple Togo kple, Nyiɖu Ƒuta kpakple Burkina Faso. Aƒu si woyɔna be Gulf of Guinea la le eƒe anyiehe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 32,833,031 lɔƒo (2016). Woɖo Gana tso Gold Coast kpakple British Togoland si nɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Gana dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le Tedoxe 6 dzi, le ƒe 1957 me. Gana ƒe fiadzue nye Accra.

    Xlẽ yi edzi le afisia.....
    Nyati Siwo Woɖe Ðe Go


    Ènyaa...?

Volta Region (Amugã Nutome) si woyɔna tsa be Togoland alo British Togoland nye Ghana ƒe nuto wuiade wo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele ɣetoɖoe kpadzi ne Togo eye le ɣedzeƒe kpadzi na Amuga tɔsisi la. Efe toxɔdue nye Ho.

images.desc:
Jerry John Rawlings si wodzi Masa 22, 1947 me, nye Ghana asrafomegã, yameʋukula, kple dunyahela si kplɔ dukɔa kpuie le ƒe 1979 me eye emegbe tso ƒe 1981 va se ɖe ƒe 2001 me. Exɔ ŋgɔ na asrafowo ƒe dziɖuɖu vaseɖe ƒe 1993 me eye emegbe wòwɔ dɔ zi eve abe Ghana ƒe dukplɔla si woti le demokrasimɔ nu ene. Eyae nye kplɔla si nɔ anyi ɣeyiɣi didi wu le Ghana ƒe ŋutinya me, eye wòɖu dukɔa dzi ƒe 19 sɔŋ. Etrɔ megbe le Adeɛmekpɔxe 12, 2020 me.
Xlẽ yi edzi le afisia...Nyati Siwo Woɖe Ðe Go

Exɔ ŋgɔ na asrafowo ƒe dziɖuɖu vaseɖe ƒe 1993 me eye emegbe wòwɔ dɔ zi eve abe Ghana ƒe dukplɔla si woti le demokrasimɔ nu ene. Eyae nye kplɔla si nɔ anyi ɣeyiɣi didi wu le Ghana ƒe ŋutinya me, eye wòɖu dukɔa dzi ƒe 19 sɔŋ. Etrɔ megbe le Adeɛmekpɔxe 12, 2020 me.

Gana nye Afrika dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo. Gana do liƒo kple Togo kple, Nyiɖu Ƒuta kpakple Burkina Faso. Aƒu si woyɔna be Gulf of Guinea la le eƒe anyiehe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 32,833,031 lɔƒo (2016).
Woɖo Gana tso Gold Coast kpakple British Togoland si nɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Gana dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le Tedoxe 6 dzi, le ƒe 1957 me. Gana ƒe fiadzue nye Accra.
Xlẽ yi edzi le afisia.....Nyati Siwo Woɖe Ðe Go

**Jerry John Rawlings** si wodzi [Masa 22](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Masa_22?action=edit&redlink=1 "Masa 22 \(wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o\)"), [1947](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/1947?action=edit&redlink=1 "1947 \(wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o\)") me, nye [Ghana](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gana "Gana") asrafomegã, yameʋukula, kple dunyahela si kplɔ dukɔa kpuie le ƒe 1979 me eye emegbe tso ƒe 1981 va se ɖe ƒe 2001 me. Exɔ ŋgɔ na asrafowo ƒe dziɖuɖu vaseɖe ƒe 1993 me eye emegbe wòwɔ dɔ zi eve abe Ghana ƒe dukplɔla si woti le demokrasimɔ nu ene. Eyae nye kplɔla si nɔ anyi ɣeyiɣi didi wu le Ghana ƒe ŋutinya me, eye wòɖu dukɔa dzi ƒe 19 sɔŋ. Etrɔ megbe le Adeɛmekpɔxe 12, 2020 me.

[![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Flag_of_Ghana.svg/250px-Flag_of_Ghana.svg.png)](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Ghana.svg)
**Gana** nye [Afrika](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afrika "Afrika") dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele [Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afrika_%C6%92e_%C9%A3eto%C9%96o%C6%92e?action=edit&redlink=1 "Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe \(wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o\)") lɔƒo. Gana do liƒo kple [Togo](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Togo "Togo") kple, [Nyiɖu Ƒuta](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nyi%C9%96u_%C6%91uta "Nyiɖu Ƒuta") kpakple [Burkina Faso](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burkina_Faso "Burkina Faso"). Aƒu si woyɔna be _[Gulf of Guinea](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gulf_of_Guinea?action=edit&redlink=1 "Gulf of Guinea \(wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o\)")_ la le eƒe anyiehe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 32,833,031 lɔƒo (2016). Woɖo Gana tso _Gold Coast_ kpakple _British Togoland_ si nɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Gana dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le Tedoxe 6 dzi, le ƒe 1957 me. Gana ƒe fiadzue nye [Accra](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Accra "Accra").

**Volta Region (Amugã Nutome)** si woyɔna tsa be [Togoland](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Togoland?action=edit&redlink=1 "Togoland \(wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o\)") alo [British Togoland](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_Togoland?action=edit&redlink=1 "British Togoland \(wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o\)") nye [Ghana](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghana "Ghana") ƒe nuto wuiade wo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele ɣetoɖoe kpadzi ne [Togo](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Togo "Togo") eye le ɣedzeƒe kpadzi na Amuga tɔsisi la. Efe toxɔdue nye [Ho](https://ee.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ho,_Ghana?action=edit&redlink=1 "Ho, Ghana \(wo me ŋlɔe haɖeke o\)").

**Jerry John Rawlings** si wodzi Masa 22⟨43⟩, 1947⟨44⟩ me, nye Ghana⟨45⟩ asrafomegã, yameʋukula, kple dunyahela si kplɔ dukɔa kpuie le ƒe 1979 me eye emegbe tso ƒe 1981 va se ɖe ƒe 2001 me. Exɔ ŋgɔ na asrafowo ƒe dziɖuɖu vaseɖe ƒe 1993 me eye emegbe wòwɔ dɔ zi eve abe Ghana ƒe dukplɔla si woti le demokrasimɔ nu ene. Eyae nye kplɔla si nɔ anyi ɣeyiɣi didi wu le Ghana ƒe ŋutinya me, eye wòɖu dukɔa dzi ƒe 19 sɔŋ. Etrɔ megbe le Adeɛmekpɔxe 12, 2020 me.

Aƒu si woyɔna be _Gulf of Guinea⟨54⟩_ la le eƒe anyiehe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 32,833,031 lɔƒo (2016). Woɖo Gana tso _Gold Coast_ kpakple _British Togoland_ si nɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Gana dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le Tedoxe 6 dzi, le ƒe 1957 me.
